  "datePublished": "2026-03-05",
  "description": "Lore is the accumulated background knowledge of a fictional world: its histories, myths, cosmologies, genealogies, natural laws, and cultural details that are not necessarily foregrounded in any single narrative but provide depth and coherence to the world as a whole. Lore is what a world knows about itself, whether or not any particular story tells it.",
